      "span_text": "The significantly increased MBL-concentration and MBL-C4-AC values in plasma from CD patients, compared to values obtained from healthy controls, are opposite to our results in plasma from CD patients complicated by fistulizing ano-rectal disease  despite their comparability in disease activity as indicated by the Harvey-Bradshaw values."
